snippet: KEATS--Sheila. The School for Strings mourns the passing of Miss Sheila Keats, the School's Co- Founder. She will be missed by all. A memorial concert will be scheduled for later this year. For more information please email: sfs--info@ schoolforstrings.org. Sincerely, The Board of Trustees, Alexander Yudkovsky, Executive Director 1/3
lead_paragraph: KEATS--Sheila. The School for Strings mourns the passing of Miss Sheila Keats, the School's Co- Founder. She will be missed by all.
